  "texts": [
    "Sentiment AnalysisSentiment analysis is the NLU task of prediction of sentiment polarity of a text.",
    "Sentiment analysis encompasses several related tasks, such as sarcasm classification and target-specific sentiment analysis.",
    "We discuss past work in sentiment analysis along four directions: experiences from annotation (which highlights the challenge of dialects for sentiment analysis), dialect-aware models, dialect-invariant models, and, finally, de-biasing of sentiment analysis models as a post-processing step.",
    "Table 4 summarises approaches for sentiment analysis.",
    "Early guessing for dialects: A recent advancement in dialect identification is early guessing [Kanjirangat et al. 2022]."
  ]
